{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC15_TAN_010.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x21,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*huff* *huff* Looks like I still have a long way to go..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc9,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "The scenery's the same, no matter how far I go. Phew, I'm exhausted..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xca,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I should take a break under the shade of that ruin..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...Heeey..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "...Huh? I thought I heard something..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...Heeeeeey...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Someone's over there...<CR>It's not an illusion, is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It looks like she's waving.<CR>I guess I'll go over there..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x12c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Wow, I'm really surprised! I never thought I'd meet a person from somewhere else in a place like this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha...me, too. I haven't seen anyone until now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Miss Cityfolk!<CR>It must've been hard to walk in<CR>those shoes!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, it was challenging, since they kept burrowing into the sand..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "The ground around here is hard, so you should take a little rest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "You're right. Maybe I should..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Phew, I think I feel a lot better.<CR>My feet feel much lighter now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "For some urban girl, I'm sure you're not used to getting your feet stuck in sand with every step..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Some merchant guy, who's a regular out here, complains about that every time he comes out here, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Wow, that merchant must be really passionate if he comes all the way out here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "He comes out here for business.<CR>What did you come here for?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I'm here...to search for something. Like...medicinal ingredients."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I'm an apothecary.<CR>My name is Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you're an apothecary!<CR>My name is Tanya!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I gather salt from this lake with my family."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Oh, salt... I see."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Salt? Here? So the white ground around here is salt!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, yup, yup! You probably use salt that we dug up every day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "No one else really sells salt."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "But enough about me!<CR>It's your turn, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I wanna hear stories about the city. Like, what's it like, and what everyone does."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, sure. Let's see, what should I talk about...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Hrrmm, I think I recovered from my<CR>fatigue with this nice long rest.<CR>I should probably get going again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "I'm glad I got to hear a lot about the city. I hope I get to see you again somewhere!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Yup, I hope so, too!"
        }
    ]
}